org.barghos.core.api.tuple

Interface ITup4fW

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITupfW
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IColor4W, IHDRColor4W, ILDRColor4W, IVec4W
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HDRColor4, LDRColor4, Tup4f, Vec4f

    public interface ITup4fW
extends ITupfW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 4-dimensional float tuple.
